    "rationale": "Linear redesigned their settings pages from the ground up with a new hierarchical structure. The old flat settings structure was replaced with organized categories: Account (personal settings), Features (workspace-level features), Administration (workspace settings for admins), and Your teams (team membership). Users previously accessed 'Features' directly from settings; now they must navigate through the new hierarchy.",
